data.description: Peace and quiet in your own 7.22 acres paradise. This beautiful 3 bed 2 bath double wide home features a large open concept kitchen-dining-living room. The kitchen has an island bar top which is great for eating at and a new dishwasher for when the meals are done. The master bedroom is split from the other two bedrooms and has it's own large master bath.  Inside you will find a garden tub with views of the beautiful country side, a glassed in shower, a his and her vanity with a large mirror, and lots of storage.  The outside features a new roof and a very large back porch which leads into a fenced area that works great for your pets.  There is also a large storage shed and lots of room to play.  Country living at its best.
